OPERANDS
     listener_id
         A unique identifier for the IIOP listener to be created.

EXAMPLES
     Example 1 Using the create-iiop-listener subcommand

     The  following  command  creates  an  IIOP  listener   named
     sample_iiop_listener:

       asadmin> create-iiop-listener --listeneraddress 192.168.1.100 --iiopport 1400 sample_iiop_listener
